===中泰網路罵戰===
{{main|2020年中泰網路罵戰}}
[[孙笑川|嗨粉文化]]流行词「NMSL」(“你妈死了”的汉语拼音简稱，全写为nǐmāsǐlē，注音符号则为ㄋㄧˇㄇㄚ ㄙˇㄌㄜ˙）在中国大陆和泰国2020年4月的[[中泰網絡罵戰|网络骂战]]中流传到海外<ref>{{cite web |title=泰國男星和女友對話　引中國網軍以台獨之名出征　泰國網民輕鬆回應「擊退」對手 |url=https://www.thestandnews.com/international/%E6%B3%B0%E5%9C%8B%E7%94%B7%E6%98%9F%E5%92%8C%E5%A5%B3%E5%8F%8B%E5%B0%8D%E8%A9%B1-%E5%BC%95%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E7%B6%B2%E8%BB%8D%E4%BB%A5%E5%8F%B0%E7%8D%A8%E4%B9%8B%E5%90%8D%E5%87%BA%E5%BE%81-%E6%B3%B0%E5%9C%8B%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E8%BC%95%E9%AC%86%E5%9B%9E%E6%87%89-%E6%93%8A%E9%80%80-%E5%B0%8D%E6%89%8B/ |website=立場新聞 |accessdate=2020-04-16 |date=2020-04-13 |archive-date=2020-04-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200423101056/https://www.thestandnews.com/international/%E6%B3%B0%E5%9C%8B%E7%94%B7%E6%98%9F%E5%92%8C%E5%A5%B3%E5%8F%8B%E5%B0%8D%E8%A9%B1-%E5%BC%95%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E7%B6%B2%E8%BB%8D%E4%BB%A5%E5%8F%B0%E7%8D%A8%E4%B9%8B%E5%90%8D%E5%87%BA%E5%BE%81-%E6%B3%B0%E5%9C%8B%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E8%BC%95%E9%AC%86%E5%9B%9E%E6%87%89-%E6%93%8A%E9%80%80-%E5%B0%8D%E6%89%8B/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，由於泰方政府素來貪污腐敗，小粉紅在攻擊泰國時，羞辱總理與泰王時反而受到泰國人讚揚和嘲笑，泰國網友還要指導和科普泰國歷來政治醜聞的相關惡搞作品，被反對者使用nmslese來形容陷入輿論戰中的小粉红，由於對雙方政治的理解錯誤，該次出擊在人數壓制後也沒有達成對戰目標下告終<ref>{{cite web |title=Nmslese |url=https://www.urbandictionary.com/define.php?term=Nmslese |website=Urban Dictionary |accessdate=2020-04-16 |archive-date=2020-05-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200523194555/https://www.urbandictionary.com/define.php?term=Nmslese |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%96%87%E6%91%98/article/20200416/s00022/1586958694421/%E4%B8%AD%E6%B3%B0%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E7%BD%B5%E6%88%B0-%E3%80%8C%E5%B0%8F%E7%B2%89%E7%B4%85%E3%80%8D%E7%9C%9F%E7%9A%84%E6%95%97%E8%B5%B0%E4%BA%86%E5%97%8E-%EF%BC%88%E6%96%87-%E9%99%B3%E5%B8%86%E5%B7%9D%EF%BC%89 |title=中泰網民罵戰 「小粉紅」真的敗走了嗎？（文：陳帆川) |access-date=2021-09-09 |archive-date=2021-09-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210909175233/https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%96%87%e6%91%98/article/20200416/s00022/1586958694421/%e4%b8%ad%e6%b3%b0%e7%b6%b2%e6%b0%91%e7%bd%b5%e6%88%b0-%e3%80%8c%e5%b0%8f%e7%b2%89%e7%b4%85%e3%80%8d%e7%9c%9f%e7%9a%84%e6%95%97%e8%b5%b0%e4%ba%86%e5%97%8e-%ef%bc%88%e6%96%87-%e9%99%b3%e5%b8%86%e5%b7%9d%ef%bc%89 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

